<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">詩</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">代書寄奉蟾上人</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other">
<milestone unit="juan" n="49"/>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0941c" n="0941c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b01"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="49"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="49"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead>閑居編第四十九</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b02"/><byline cb:type="author">宋孤山沙門　智圓　著</byline>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">湖居感傷</cb:mulu><head>湖居感傷<note place="inline">五十四韻</note></head>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b04"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0941c0401"><l>迷真渺無始<caesura/>飄業產錢唐<caesura/>外族宗南郡</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b05"/><l>門風祖偃王<caesura/>微緣先劫種<caesura/>宿習妙齡彰</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b06"/><l>父母憐多病<caesura/>親賓怪異常<caesura/>布花模講道</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b07"/><l>畵石斆題章<caesura/>戒印齓年佩<caesura/>心猿志學狂</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b08"/><l>榮名虗準擬<caesura/>簪組妄思量<caesura/>禮樂師周孔</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b09"/><l>虗無學老莊<caesura/>躁嫌成器<g ref="#CB15085"/><caesura/>心競寸陰忙</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b10"/><l>翼翼修天爵<caesura/>孜孜恥面牆<caesura/>內藏儒志氣</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b11"/><l>外假佛衣裳<caesura/>每惡銷金口<caesura/>時勞疾惡腸</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b12"/><l>手中期得桂<caesura/>箭下待穿楊<caesura/>騃鹿方隨<g ref="#CB08504"/></l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b13"/><l>堅冰忽遇陽<caesura/>繫珠知在體<caesura/>甘露忝親甞</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b14"/><l>要道傳三觀<caesura/>真機得妙常<caesura/>不然心跡火</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b15"/><l>任結<g ref="#CB15150"/>根霜<caesura/>覺路雙輪駕<caesura/>真空兩翅翔</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b16"/><l>飢來還遇饍<caesura/>渴去<note n="0941c1601" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【卍續】</note><app n="0941c1601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>逢漿<caesura/>靜處如來室</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b17"/><l>高眠解脫床<caesura/>理高山峭<g ref="#CB15072"/><caesura/>道大海汪洋</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0203b18"/><l>力戰魔軍散<caesura/>功扶佛化昌<caesura/>空山憐寂寂</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a01"/><l>塵路笑茫茫<caesura/>觸境知無著<caesura/>閑居貴坐忘</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a02"/><l>消搖希自了<caesura/>言說亦何妨<caesura/>撰疏松牕冷</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a03"/><l>揮松古殿涼<caesura/>來蒙隨力化<caesura/>真誥應機揚</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a04"/><l>達理雖云短<caesura/>尋文或有長<caesura/>圓伊令了悟</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a05"/><l>法愛教消亡<caesura/>性任融凡聖<caesura/>修宜示否臧</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0941c24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a06"/><l>冥心潛應夢<caesura/>取驗敢垂祥<caesura/>事佛身多累</l>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0942a" n="0942a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a07"/><l>為師道實荒<caesura/>衡門連竹石<caesura/>草屋帶林塘</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a08"/><l>冬服和絺<g ref="#CB06668"/><caesura/>中飡乏稻梁<caesura/>水邊雲作伴</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a09"/><l>巖下柏為香<caesura/>景物看無猒<caesura/>幽棲興未央</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a10"/><l><g ref="#CB15085"/>籬啼翡翠<caesura/>春沼浴鴛鴦<caesura/>菡萏花如畵</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a11"/><l>嶔崟岫若糚<caesura/>飄牕松韻淡<caesura/>翻砌菊花黃</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a12"/><l>放<g ref="#CB15112"/>時登嶺<caesura/>觀魚或在梁<caesura/>豈愁身病害</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a13"/><l>長喜世平康<caesura/>無處求煩惱<caesura/>隨時任寂光</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a14"/><l>昏衢懸慧日<caesura/>苦海泛慈航<caesura/>誓坐菩提樹</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a15"/><l>高躋寂滅場<caesura/>冥真周法界<caesura/>垂應徧諸方</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a16"/><l>頓漸門皆<g ref="#CB15035"/><caesura/>偏圓藥盡良<caesura/>驚迷辯雷震</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a17"/><l>摧惑法輪疆<caesura/>鷲嶺先開會<caesura/>金河後祕藏</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204a18"/><l>留形歸後德<caesura/>遺法益無疆<caesura/>四等心彌廣</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b01"/><l>三慈化甚詳<caesura/>道齊諸妙覺<caesura/>事類釋迦皇</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b02"/><l>生滅非吾土<caesura/>圓澄是故鄉<caesura/>一空長寂寂</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b03"/><l>萬類本惶惶<caesura/>庶了無生旨<caesura/>無生更可傷</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">讀清塞集</cb:mulu><head>讀清塞集</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b05"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0942a1701"><l>立意造平淡<caesura/>冥搜出眾情<caesura/>何人知所得</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b06"/><l>後世謾傳名<caesura/>雲樹飢猨斷<caesura/>冰潭片月傾</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b07"/><l>如無子期聽<caesura/>綠綺為誰鳴</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">寄趙璞</cb:mulu><head>寄趙璞</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b09"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0942a2101"><l>故鄉勾踐國<caesura/>解印掛帆歸<caesura/>吟苦容雖瘦</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b10"/><l>官清道自肥<caesura/>堂幽山屐在<caesura/>厨冷甑塵飛</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b11"/><l>莫向雲門下<caesura/>高歌便採薇</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0942a24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">山中與友人夜話</cb:mulu><head>山中與友人夜話</head>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0942b" n="0942b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b13"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0942b0101"><l>草舍閑宵坐<caesura/>消搖事可評<caesura/>澄心防有著</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b14"/><l>深隱貴無名<caesura/>砌月移松影<caesura/>風泉混磬聲</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b15"/><l>共期吾道在<caesura/>萬事任營營</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">閑居書事</cb:mulu><head>閑居書事</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b17"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0942b0501"><l>淡然忘外事<caesura/>林下自怡情<caesura/>室冷秋苔色</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0204b18"/><l>軒閑夜月明<caesura/>眠雲慙道薄<caesura/>餌藥覺身輕</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a01"/><l>擬學鴟夷子<caesura/>時時變姓名</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">禹廟</cb:mulu><head>禹廟</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a03"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0942b0901"><l>洪水不為害<caesura/>黎元受賜多<caesura/>道尊由揖讓</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a04"/><l>功大匪干戈<caesura/>任上諸侯貢<caesura/>貽謀五子歌</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a05"/><l>稽山千古在<caesura/>宮闕倚嵳峩</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">早行</cb:mulu><head>早行</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a07"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0942b1301"><l>杖錫無同侶<caesura/>衝霜獨自行<caesura/>斷橋殘月在</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a08"/><l>孤店曉鷄鳴<caesura/>灌木樓禽散<caesura/>荒原宿霧平</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a09"/><l>迴觀遠山色<caesura/><note n="0942b1501" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【卍續】</note><app n="0942b1501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>覺太陽明</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">江上聞笛</cb:mulu><head>江上聞笛</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a11"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0942b1701"><l>夜久聞橫笛<caesura/>寥寥景更賖<caesura/>天容垂極岸</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a12"/><l>月色冷平沙<caesura/>靜引鄉心遠<caesura/>閑驚旅<g ref="#CB15150"/>華</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a13"/><l>哀音殊未<note n="0942b1901" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【卍續】</note><app n="0942b1901"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app><caesura/>何處落梅花</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">詠鷰</cb:mulu><head>詠鷰</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a15"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0942b2101"><l>來去知時候<caesura/>堪憐異眾禽<caesura/>雙飛春雨細</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a16"/><l>對語畵堂深<caesura/>寄宿鵰梁穩<caesura/><g ref="#CB00081"/>泥柳岸陰</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a17"/><l>捿身自有處<caesura/>鷹集莫相侵</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0942b24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205a18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">讀杜牧集</cb:mulu><head>讀杜牧集</head>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0942c" n="0942c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b01"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0942c0101"><l>讒<g ref="#CB02439"/>當面唾<caesura/>輕生不得殳<caesura/>去邪空有志</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b02"/><l>嫉惡奈無徒<caesura/>後世名垂遠<caesura/>當時道亦孤</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b03"/><l>荒齋獨懷感<caesura/>殘日照庭蕪</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">寄題聰上人房庭竹</cb:mulu><head>寄題聰上人房庭竹</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b05"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0942c0501"><l>結根依靜砌<caesura/>蕭灑映禪房<caesura/>高節欺群木</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b06"/><l>青陰過短墻<caesura/>夜聲喧夢枕<caesura/>秋露滴琴床</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b07"/><l>遙想添吟思<caesura/>閑觀到夕陽</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">武肅廟</cb:mulu><head>武肅廟</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b09"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0942c0901"><l>土德衰微後<caesura/>忠誠道不群<caesura/>誓功陳帶礪</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b10"/><l>霸業擬桓文<caesura/>妙略姧雄懾<caesura/>英聲四海聞</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b11"/><l>山旁遺廟在<caesura/>牢落閉深雲</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">寄蜀川王道士</cb:mulu><head>寄蜀川王道士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b13"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0942c1301"><l><g ref="#CB15112"/>賀幾遲留<caesura/>岷峩水石幽<caesura/>御風同列子</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b14"/><l>夢蝶擬莊周<caesura/>醉臥空林月<caesura/>狂歌古觀秋</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b15"/><l>何時歸閬苑<caesura/>閑共老仙游</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">寄道士</cb:mulu><head>寄道士</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b17"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0942c1701"><l>長聞披<g ref="#CB15112"/>氅<caesura/>城市往來頻<caesura/>得道人難測</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0205b18"/><l>和光跡易親<caesura/>堂閑秋擣藥<caesura/>壇冷夜朝真</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a01"/><l>幾憶蓬壺頂<caesura/>蟠桃爛漫春</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">寄定海許少府</cb:mulu><head>寄定海許少府</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a03"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0942c2101"><l>見說梅仙邑<caesura/>波濤接杳冥<caesura/>訟庭秋蘚合</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a04"/><l>吟閣海雲醒<caesura/>愛月宵留客<caesura/>尋僧晝掩扃</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a05"/><l>公餘幽興在<caesura/>時夢故山青</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0942c24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">寄若訥上人</cb:mulu><head>寄若訥上人</head>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0943a" n="0943a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a07"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0943a0101"><l>江濵方話別<caesura/>倏忽十年餘<caesura/>感舊空闕夢</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a08"/><l>閑眠懶寄書<caesura/>砌涼鳴蟋蟀<caesura/>潭冷照蟾蜍</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a09"/><l>北望滄波闊<caesura/>無由訪所居</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">山中尋羽客不遇</cb:mulu><head>山中尋羽客不遇</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a11"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0943a0501"><l>杖黎尋隱跡<caesura/>重疊過林泉<caesura/>花暖幽禽語</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a12"/><l>堂空瑞獸眠<caesura/><g ref="#CB00589"/>松寒有韻<caesura/>茶竈冷無煙</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a13"/><l>知在何峯頂<caesura/>高談會列仙</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">送人南遊</cb:mulu><head>送人南遊</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a15"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0943a0901"><l>難阻南遊興<caesura/>酣歌出故林<caesura/>路分滄海闊</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a16"/><l>山疊瘴雲深<caesura/>馬援<g ref="#CB15156"/>寧在<caesura/>重華廟可尋</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a17"/><l>他年却歸此<caesura/>閑話學夷音</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206a18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">懷同志</cb:mulu><head>懷同志</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b01"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0943a1301"><l>孤吟成白首<caesura/>十載別同聲<caesura/>海國書難到</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b02"/><l>空堂夢易成<caesura/>淳風心共樂<caesura/>直道世多輕</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b03"/><l>未卜重相見<caesura/>波濤萬里程</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">聞蛩</cb:mulu><head>聞蛩</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b05"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0943a1701"><l>沉沉向秋暮<caesura/>切切聲相續<caesura/>夜靜草堂深</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a18"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b06"/><l>閑牀照孤燭</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a19"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">湖上閑坐</cb:mulu><head>湖上閑坐</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a20"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b08"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0943a2001"><l>終日湖亭坐<caesura/>悠悠萬慮閑<caesura/>眼前何所有</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a21"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b09"/><l>寒水與秋山</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a22"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">池上</cb:mulu><head>池上</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a23"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b11"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0943a2301"><l>漚生復漚滅<caesura/>水濕元無異<caesura/>盡日倚欄看</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943a24"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b12"/><l>無人知此意</l></lg></cb:div>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X56.0949.0943b" n="0943b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b01"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">草堂即事</cb:mulu><head>草堂即事</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b02"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b14"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0943b0201"><l>經歲人不到<caesura/>騰騰養疎拙<caesura/>心期物外閑</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b03"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b15"/><l>緣向漚中絕<caesura/>入室容清風<caesura/>升堂許明月</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b04"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b16"/><l>空庭何所有<caesura/>冷落唯松雪</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b05"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">讀楞嚴經</cb:mulu><head>讀楞嚴經</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b06"/><lb ed="R101" n="0206b18"/><lg xml:id="lgX56p0943b0601"><l>案上楞嚴典<caesura/>時看浣病愁<caesura/>階閑移短影</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b07"/><lb ed="R101" n="0207a01"/><l>牕<caesura/>冷值高秋<caesura/>眼病花無菓<caesura/>心狂照失頭</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b08"/><lb ed="R101" n="0207a02"/><l>指空期識月<caesura/>認指更悠悠</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b09"/><lb ed="R101" n="0207a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">病中懷石壁行紹上人</cb:mulu><head>病中懷石壁行紹上人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b10"/><lb ed="R101" n="0207a04"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0943b1001"><l>石壁春歸去<caesura/>孤山秋未來<caesura/>夜深扶病坐</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b11"/><lb ed="R101" n="0207a05"/><l>明月照蒼苔</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b12"/><lb ed="R101" n="0207a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">謝可孜上人惠楞嚴般若二經并治脾藥</cb:mulu><head>謝可孜上人惠楞嚴般若二經并治脾藥</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b13"/><lb ed="R101" n="0207a07"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgX56p0943b1301"><l>經妙蕩煩惑<caesura/>藥靈醫病身<caesura/>道明無去住</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b14"/><lb ed="R101" n="0207a08"/><l>方驗有君臣<caesura/>靜翫知心寂<caesura/>時飡覺氣均</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b15"/><lb ed="R101" n="0207a09"/><l>徘徊感知<note n="0943b1501" resp="CBETA" type="add">己【CB】，巳【卍續】</note><app n="0943b1501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">己</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app><caesura/>於我分彌親</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b16"/><lb ed="R101" n="0207a10"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0943b17"/><lb ed="R101" n="0207a11"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="49"><cb:jhead>閑居編第四十九</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</cb:div></body></text></TEI>